
Overview of noun lightning

The noun lightning has 2 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                      
1. (8) lightning -- (abrupt electric discharge from cloud to cloud or from cloud to earth accompanied by the emission of light)
2. (3) lightning -- (the flash of light that accompanies an electric discharge in the atmosphere (or something resembling such a flash); can scintillate for a second or more)
